history.text: Hello, how are you? Have you read about any good movies lately?
Yeah, great director by Joss Whedon
Cool. I have seen some of his movies and they were good. Is this one similar to ones he has made in the past?
Hes very known for superhero genre
Yes, that is correct. What did you read about his new movie? Did it get good reviews?

The rating on rotten Tomatoes
  is 92%
Wow that is very good. Sounds like a movie I want to watch. Do you know what genre the movie is? It is another superhero movie?
The genre is a drama/superhero staring Robert Downey Jr and Chris Evans
Sounds like a new Avengers movie! I love those. Have you seen the old Avenger movies or the new one that you read about?
I have seen them all.  Have you read the marvel comics?
I have only read a few here and there. I don't know much about them though. Have you read them? Do you think the movies are similar to the comics?
